oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jokes Told By Hank Snow and Friends
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording contains Hank Snow, Bobby Sykes, and Chubby Wise telling crude jokes. The tape is dated March 18, 1957. This tape is fifty-one of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow; Chubby Wise; Bobby Sykes;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) Unidentified guitar tune (Unidentified) [incomplete] -- (00:13) Bobby Sykes comes on midway through a crude joke -- (02:11) Snow asks Bobby to tell a different joke -- (02:34) Sykes tells another crude joke -- (05:55) Laughter and comments from the men -- (06:04) Another crude joke from Sykes about a parrot -- (07:35) Sykes tells another crude joke, similar to the first joke told -- (08:52) Comments from the men and rummaging noises -- (09:15) Another crude joke with a parrot -- (12:24) Laughter from the men -- (12:47) Crude joke from Chubby Wise -- (14:29) A crude joke from Hank Snow -- (17:28) The men try to figure out another joke to tell [quiet] -- (18:21) Laughter -- (18:30) Wise starting to tell another crude joke [quiet with someone tapping] -- (20:05) Laughter -- (20:11) Sykes tells crude jokes about nudist colonies -- (21:14) Wise tells a crude joke -- (22:05) Laughter and overlapped conversation -- (22:35) Talking about nudist colonies again -- (23:54) Overlapped conversation -- (24:06) Another crude joke from Sykes -- (26:00) Snow tells another crude joke -- (27:51) Wise tells another crude joke [quiet and talking in the background] -- (28:47) Last crude joke told by Snow -- (20:26) Men say goodbye
